<div><head>《太康地記》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a.2">并州不以衛水為號，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a.3">又不以恆山為名，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a.4">而云并者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a.5">蓋以其在兩谷之間乎。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a.6">韓、魏、趙謂之三晉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a.7">并、冀二州是其地也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a.8">青州，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a.9">東方少陽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a.10">其色青，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a.11">其氣清，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a.12">歲之首，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a.13">事之始也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-1a.14">故以為名。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-2a.2">雍州兼得梁州之地，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-2a.3">西北之位，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-2a.4">陽所不及，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-2a.5">陰氣擁閼，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-2a.6">故取名焉。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-2a.7">奉高者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-2a.8">以事東岳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-2a.9">帝王禪代之處也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-2a.10">故明當在縣南四里，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-2a.11">漢武立大壇於東山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-2a.12">以登天下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1675_CHANT_001-2a.13">示增高。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
